  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/d0e020a31e6bb38e5e77c552910dc722.avif?t=1774515014\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强者群英传是一个单人的回合制战斗冒险游戏，内含大量的养成内容，通过不断击败更强的对手完成主角的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个过程中你会收获许多同伴，宝物，还可以把击败过的对手招募进自己的阵营。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开始漫长的冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一艘巨大的飞船上决定你接下里的行动方针。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/7d40b6d7cd417b79ffa4bc4ca734ae70.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/7d40b6d7cd417b79ffa4bc4ca734ae70.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的地图系统，包含了时间、昼夜、光照、天气、环境5种混合效果</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图区分室内与室外，大雨不会下进阴森的洞窟里，森林会飘落树叶，时间划分出昼夜两种视觉风格，这个世界看起来生机勃勃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/e3f219db141066b1e0304d108b71a95a.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/e3f219db141066b1e0304d108b71a95a.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/5c510eba3fc740721511eb1d3c297f68.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/5c510eba3fc740721511eb1d3c297f68.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鲜艳而多变的战斗场景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的环境下进入战斗，场景也会发生变化，昼夜的变换，清晨的阳光，飘落的白雪也会影响到战斗中去，这一切只为呈现丰富的视觉效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/90a80071bb95b0872111fe8912f2d5e9.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/90a80071bb95b0872111fe8912f2d5e9.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/4d64abbb0c507da567bc38638695ab53.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/4d64abbb0c507da567bc38638695ab53.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地图遇敌采用明雷设计，朝你进攻的单位会有文字指示</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保证你不会出现空气遇敌的场景，你可以通过走位避开你不想对战的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏有手动操作、自动战斗 2种模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手动操作战斗会像传统的RPG游戏一样，自动战斗更像自走棋，即使你不理解战斗系统也能进行战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打败强敌收集宝物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不断的战斗打造一支强大团队，在超过500种战斗情景下挑战强敌，并且击败它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次战斗的遇敌都是随机刷新的，同样的敌人遇见2次会以不同的组合、位置随机出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/8217bfe723ec573529924b91ba7db30c.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/8217bfe723ec573529924b91ba7db30c.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏里有50名待加入的同伴，敌人，昔日的对手也会成为今日的伙伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带着你的团队在这个名为强者世界的地方完成主角的使命吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >详细功能：包括但不限于……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机奖池</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不重样的对手</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手动、自动战斗模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动存档</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全地图飞空术-你可以通过大地图去到游戏中的每一张地图（需要激活传送点）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加速功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物图鉴（在战斗中查看当前对手的属性、克制关系）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道具图鉴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一键恢复（你需要准备足够多的回复道具）</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/d0e020a31e6bb38e5e77c552910dc722.avif?t=1774515014\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强者群英传是一个单人的回合制战斗冒险游戏，内含大量的养成内容，通过不断击败更强的对手完成主角的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个过程中你会收获许多同伴，宝物，还可以把击败过的对手招募进自己的阵营。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开始漫长的冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一艘巨大的飞船上决定你接下里的行动方针。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/7d40b6d7cd417b79ffa4bc4ca734ae70.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/7d40b6d7cd417b79ffa4bc4ca734ae70.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的地图系统，包含了时间、昼夜、光照、天气、环境5种混合效果</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图区分室内与室外，大雨不会下进阴森的洞窟里，森林会飘落树叶，时间划分出昼夜两种视觉风格，这个世界看起来生机勃勃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/e3f219db141066b1e0304d108b71a95a.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/e3f219db141066b1e0304d108b71a95a.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/5c510eba3fc740721511eb1d3c297f68.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/5c510eba3fc740721511eb1d3c297f68.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鲜艳而多变的战斗场景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的环境下进入战斗，场景也会发生变化，昼夜的变换，清晨的阳光，飘落的白雪也会影响到战斗中去，这一切只为呈现丰富的视觉效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/90a80071bb95b0872111fe8912f2d5e9.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/90a80071bb95b0872111fe8912f2d5e9.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/4d64abbb0c507da567bc38638695ab53.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/4d64abbb0c507da567bc38638695ab53.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地图遇敌采用明雷设计，朝你进攻的单位会有文字指示</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保证你不会出现空气遇敌的场景，你可以通过走位避开你不想对战的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏有手动操作、自动战斗 2种模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手动操作战斗会像传统的RPG游戏一样，自动战斗更像自走棋，即使你不理解战斗系统也能进行战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打败强敌收集宝物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不断的战斗打造一支强大团队，在超过500种战斗情景下挑战强敌，并且击败它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次战斗的遇敌都是随机刷新的，同样的敌人遇见2次会以不同的组合、位置随机出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras/8217bfe723ec573529924b91ba7db30c.avif?t=1774515014\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461160/extras_big/8217bfe723ec573529924b91ba7db30c.avif?t=1774515014 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏里有50名待加入的同伴，敌人，昔日的对手也会成为今日的伙伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带着你的团队在这个名为强者世界的地方完成主角的使命吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >详细功能：包括但不限于……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机奖池</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不重样的对手</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手动、自动战斗模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动存档</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全地图飞空术-你可以通过大地图去到游戏中的每一张地图（需要激活传送点）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加速功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物图鉴（在战斗中查看当前对手的属性、克制关系）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道具图鉴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一键恢复（你需要准备足够多的回复道具）</p>",
